{"tid":313303,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"窮人咪撚生仔 害撚死下一代","createTime":"2017-07-08T08:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T16:54:08.000Z","uid":66731,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d094a43a967e8aee2f15d4611d30433e75475904","tid":313303,"uid":66731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T08:22:44.000Z","msg":"呢個時代 窮人老豆老母唔撚識諗<br />\n見住一個家庭 有2老 有2個仔 <br />\n大仔結婚同老婆一齊搬埋入去得2百幾呎<br />\n細仔就係我既病人<br />\n<br />\n細仔仲讀梗中學<br />\n由於一直以來都逼係一張床<br />\n生活環境差 屋企中三開始已經無再比錢佢食飯坐車<br />\n佢日日由彩虹行路去藍田返學<br />\n佢又唔識表達自己 屈埋屈埋最後有嚴重抑鬱症+自殺傾向<br />\n見到好心酸<br />\n<br />\n窮人唔好生啦 好嗎！"},{"pid":"b48fef7b2c3bbc8d72fe2c153dbd62935dfcd287","tid":313303,"uid":66731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T08:27:44.000Z","msg":"唔明點解窮人都要生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明自己都養唔掂"},{"pid":"054162e448255a9a2e3c925cc8fe9acb1f7efec6","tid":313303,"uid":46254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T08:28:55.000Z","msg":"唔生攞唔到咁多綜援<br />\n有怕又可以攞多啲<br />\n屌佢老味"},{"pid":"0758a4d1da8f7684d724798e7f50f520e90b1e24","tid":313303,"uid":102198,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T08:36:50.000Z","msg":"而家反而變到有錢唔生窮撚生"},{"pid":"6d7b2bbf72330493be2c94ece4722335251d49b0","tid":313303,"uid":66731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T09:25:29.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"c5de227e735d6e2e90cacc489e45c545c40e33a7","tid":313303,"uid":92628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T11:49:23.000Z","msg":"好心酸，唔敢想像佢既成長經歷<br />\n我地理所當然既享受，對佢黎講係幾奢侈"},{"pid":"1207ab77c85206a2b0e5154d7daf5cb28978529e","tid":313303,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T12:37:12.000Z","msg":"悲慘世界"},{"pid":"910ebfd3163dca3507067305a709cd4365cb267d","tid":313303,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T15:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔死大左就會變成毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e38cb056fdcde6bdff4e6671b4503140bf6616","tid":313303,"uid":66731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T16:54:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}